<p id="#Gene_therapy"></p>
<p><br /><br /></p>
<p class="header_box">Gene therapy</p>

<p>Riboswitches regulate gene expression by inducing (ON-switches) or repressing (OFF-switches) gene expression. Take ON-switches for example, in their native form, cause the degradation of the mRNA, thus stopping gene expression. Therefore, riboswitches can be used as a powerful tool to control gene expression in gene therapy. <br /></p>
<p id="#Gene_therapy"></p>
